@page "/components/data-table"

<PageTitle>Data Table</PageTitle>

<RzArticle ProseWidth="ProseWidth.UltraWide">
    <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H1">Data Table</RzHeading>
    <RzParagraph>
        <code>RzDataTable&lt;TItem&gt;</code> is an SSR-first table that renders a usable initial page on the server,
        then progressively enhances with Alpine + TanStack Table for client-memory sorting, search, pagination,
        visibility, and selection.
    </RzParagraph>

    <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2">Key requirements</RzHeading>
    <ul>
        <li>Stable row key is mandatory via <code>RowKey</code>.</li>
        <li>Use declarative <code>DataTableColumn&lt;TItem&gt;</code> children.</li>
        <li>Global search only uses columns with <code>Searchable=&quot;true&quot;</code>.</li>
        <li><code>InitialColumnVisibility</code> overrides per-column <code>Visible</code> for matching ids.</li>
    </ul>

    <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2">Events</RzHeading>
    <RzParagraph>
        Browser events are dispatched as <code>rz:datatable:*</code>: ready, sort-change, page-change,
        search-change, column-visibility-change, selection-change, row-click, and state-change.
    </RzParagraph>

    <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2">Client templates</RzHeading>
    <RzParagraph>
        <code>ClientTemplate</code> content is emitted once as inert templates and cloned client-side.
        Template scope provides <code>row</code>, <code>column</code>, and <code>cell</code>.
        This is not a live server-side <code>RenderFragment&lt;TItem&gt;</code> rendering model.
    </RzParagraph>

    <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2">When not to use</RzHeading>
    <RzParagraph>
        For very large datasets, server paging, grouping, expansion, or virtualization workflows, use a dedicated
        server-driven table experience instead of this v1 client-memory component.
    </RzParagraph>

    <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor">
&lt;RzDataTable TItem="UserRow"
             Items="Users"
             RowKey="u =&gt; u.Id"
             Search="true"
             SelectionMode="DataTableSelectionMode.Multiple"&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserRow" Id="name" HeaderText="Name" Field="u =&gt; u.Name" Sortable="true" Searchable="true" /&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserRow" Id="email" HeaderText="Email" Field="u =&gt; u.Email" Searchable="true" /&gt;
&lt;/RzDataTable&gt;
    </RzCodeViewer>
</RzArticle>
